OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry through
OL,6,Fthe evening, quite cloudy at first but
OL,7,Fwith increasingly clear skies. Staying
OL,8,Fmostly dry overnight, with just the
OL,9,Fodd shower possible around dawn.
OL,10,FBreezy, especially around the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FMost of the day will be dry,
OL,13,Fsome hazy sunshine in the morning.
OL,14,FRain will spread east during the
OL,15,Fevening. Warm in any sunshine inland.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,18,Fbright Wednesday morning, cloudier
OL,19,Fwith patchy rain later. Cooler with
OL,20,Fsunshine and showers on Thursday. Rain
OL,21,Flikely on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
